    {
      "id": "5b0fc391-1d17-4d97-8d77-8b1298ff62ba",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use a Dynamic SEM model to create an integrated temporal model that is meant to estimate motivation of students from video-watching behavior. Results show that there are patterns in video-watching behavior that can determine student performance.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
